Honourable Menenius, my boy Marcius
approaches;
for the love of Juno, let's go.

We hope to find you our friend;
and therefore
give you our voices heartily.

sp.l:
He approaches: you shall hear him.
Enter CORIOLANUS, marching with drum and colours;
Commoners being with him.
